            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EMeditation%20is%20not%20the%20process%20of%20clearing%20your%20mind%2C%20but%20of%20filling%20your%20mind%20with%20truth.%20It%20is%20like%20a%20rock%20displacing%20water%20in%20a%20vessel.%20Your%20mind%20is%20exposed%20continually%20to%20the%20doubt%2C%20atrocities%2C%20filth%2C%20and%20strife%20of%20the%20world%20around%20you.%20Trying%20to%20clear%20out%20those%20thoughts%20is%20very%20difficult%2C%20but%20there%20is%20a%20remedy%3A%20meditation%20upon%20God's%20Word.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIt%20takes%20a%20conscious%20effort%20to%20focus%20your%20mind%20and%20heart%20upon%20the%20truth%20of%20God's%20Word.%20Once%20you%20do%2C%20however%2C%20you%20will%20reap%20the%20benefits.%20Joshua%201%3A8%20says%2C%20%22Study%20this%20Book%20of%20the%20Law%20continually.%20Meditate%20on%20it%20day%20and%20night%20so%20you%20may%20be%20sure%20to%20obey%20all%20that%20is%20written%20in%20it.%20Only%20then%20will%20you%20succeed.%22%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EReading%20the%20Bible%20is%20good%2C%20but%20meditation%20is%20life%20changing%2C%20for%20it%20involves%20thinking%20about%20a%20verse%20until%20it%20drops%20from%20your%20mind%20into%20your%20heart.%20The%20root%20word%20meditate%20means%20%22to%20mutter%2C%22%20or%20%22to%20utter.%22%20The%20more%20you%20speak%20the%20Word%2C%20the%20more%20it%20drops%20into%20your%20spirit.%20As%20you%20go%20about%20your%20daily%20business%2C%20speak%20the%20Word%20to%20yourself.%20Continually%20%22mutter%22%20it%2C%20mulling%20it%20over%20in%20your%20mind.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWhatever%20your%20area%20of%20need%2C%20select%20several%20promises%20that%20apply%20to%20your%20situation%20and%20memorize%20them.%20Then%20meditate%20on%20them%20all%20day%20long%20(Psalm%20119%3A97).%20When%20doubt%2C%20fear%2C%20discouragement%2C%20and%20strife%20enter%20your%20mind%2C%20%22think%20about%20things%20that%20are%20excellent%20and%20worthy%20of%20praise%22%20(Philippians%204%3A8).%20Your%20faith%20will%20grow%2C%20your%20mind%20will%20change%2C%20and%20your%20way%20will%20become%20successful!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
