            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3E2%20Samuel%2014%3A1-15%3A22%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_14_1%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2214%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3E2%20Samuel%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EJoab%20Arranges%20for%20Absalom%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Return%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EJoab%20realized%20how%20much%20the%20king%20longed%20to%20see%20Absalom.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_14_2%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2214%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20he%20sent%20for%20a%20woman%20from%20Tekoa%20who%20had%20a%20reputation%20for%20great%20wisdom.%20He%20said%20to%20her%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BPretend%20you%20are%20in%20mourning%3B%20wear%20mourning%20clothes%20and%20don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20put%20on%20lotions.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E14%3A2%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Edon%26%23x2019%3Bt%20anoint%20yourself%20with%20oil.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Act%20like%20a%20woman%20who%20has%20been%20mourning%20for%20the%20dead%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_14_3%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2214%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20go%20to%20the%20king%20and%20tell%20him%20the%20story%20I%20am%20about%20to%20tell%20you.%26%23x201D%3B%20Then%20Joab%20told%20her%20what%20to%20say.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_14_4%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2214%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20the%20woman%20from%20Tekoa%20approached%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E14%3A4%3C%2Fspan%3E%20As%20in%20many%20Hebrew%20manuscripts%20and%20Greek%20and%20Syriac%20versions%3B%20Masoretic%20Text%20reads%20%3Cem%3Espoke%20to.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20the%20king%2C%20she%20bowed%20with%20her%20face%20to%20the%20ground%20in%20deep%20respect%20and%20cried%20out%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BO%26%23xA0%3Bking!%20Help%20me!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_14_5%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2214%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BWhat%26%23x2019%3Bs%20the%20trouble%3F%26%23x201D%3B%20the%20king%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BAlas%2C%20I%20am%20a%20widow!%26%23x201D%3B%20she%20replied.%20%26%23x201C%3BMy%20husband%20is%20dead.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_14_6%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2214%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EMy%20two%20sons%20had%20a%20fight%20out%20in%20the%20field.%20And%20since%20no%20one%20was%20there%20to%20stop%20it%2C%20one%20of%20them%20was%20killed.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_14_7%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2214%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3ENow%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20family%20is%20demanding%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BLet%20us%20have%20your%20son.%20We%20will%20execute%20him%20for%20murdering%20his%20brother.%20He%20doesn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20deserve%20to%20inherit%20his%20family%26%23x2019%3Bs%20property.%26%23x2019%3B%20They%20want%20to%20extinguish%20the%20only%20coal%20I%20have%20left%2C%20and%20my%20husband%26%23x2019%3Bs%20name%20and%20family%20will%20disappear%20from%20the%20face%20of%20the%20earth.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_14_8%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2214%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BLeave%20it%20to%20me%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20the%20king%20told%20her.%20%26%23x201C%3BGo%20home%2C%20and%20I%26%23x2019%3Bll%20see%20to%20it%20that%20no%20one%20touches%20him.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_14_9%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2214%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BOh%2C%20thank%20you%2C%20my%20lord%20the%20king%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20the%20woman%20from%20Tekoa%20replied.%20%26%23x201C%3BIf%20you%20are%20criticized%20for%20helping%20me%2C%20let%20the%20blame%20fall%20on%20me%20and%20on%20my%20father%26%23x2019%3Bs%20house%2C%20and%20let%20the%20king%20and%20his%20throne%20be%20innocent.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_14_10%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2214%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BIf%20anyone%20objects%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20the%20king%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3Bbring%20him%20to%20me.%20I%20can%20assure%20you%20he%20will%20never%20harm%20you%20again!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_14_11%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%2214%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20she%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BPlease%20swear%20to%20me%20by%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20that%20you%20won%26%23x2019%3Bt%20let%20anyone%20take%20vengeance%20against%20my%20son.%20I%20want%20no%20more%20bloodshed.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BAs%20surely%20as%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20lives%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20he%20replied%2C%20%26%23x201C%3Bnot%20a%20hair%20on%20your%20son%26%23x2019%3Bs%20head%20will%20be%20disturbed!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C